<b>Key Features:</b> <br>
Live, 1:1 Instruction:
Students receive personalized attention from trained teachers with CS/IT backgrounds. <br>
Curriculum: <br>
Codingal's curriculum is structured and well-designed, encouraging problem-solving and critical thinking. <br>
Project-Based Learning: <br>
Students learn by building real-world projects, such as apps, games, and websites, applying their coding knowledge.  <br>
Interactive Learning: <br>
The platform utilizes interactive and engaging methods, including quizzes, coding challenges, and video tutorials.  <br>
Experienced Instructors: <br>
Codingal boasts a team of experienced instructors who understand how children learn and can tailor their teaching approach.  <br>
Diverse Courses: <br>
They offer a range of courses, including Scratch, Python, Java, App Development, Web Development, and more.  <br>
Flexible Learning: <br>
Codingal provides flexible scheduling and customized curriculum options. <br> 
Supportive Environment: <br>
Codingal aims to create a supportive learning environment where students can thrive.  <br>
AI and Human Tutors: <br>
They aim to build a large programming school for kids and teens, leveraging both AI and human tutors. <br> 
Premium Learning Program (Codingal Prime): <br>
This program offers additional benefits like private tutoring, flexible timings, unlimited doubt sessions, and more. <br>
 A 96-lesson coding curriculum designed for kids and teens to master coding skills, fostering creativity and technical proficiency.
